<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🚨 MOMENTO OBRA VIA VIARIA 🚨</title>
    <style>
        /* Estilos Globales Goofy */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #ff00ff; /* Rosa chillón */
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(45deg, #00ffff 25%, transparent 25%), 
                linear-gradient(-45deg, #00ffff 25%, transparent 25%), 
                linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 75%, #00ffff 75%), 
                linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 75%, #00ffff 75%);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            background-position: 0 0, 0 20px, 20px -20px, -20px 0;
            font-family: "Comic Sans MS", "Chalkboard SE", sans-serif;
            color: #000;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Barra de peligro animada */
        .hazard-bar {
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                -45deg,
                #000,
                #000 20px,
                #ffcc00 20px,
                #ffcc00 40px
            );
            height: 30px;
            width: 100%;
            animation: slide 2s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes slide {
            from { background-position: 0 0; }
            to { background-position: 57px 0; }
        }

        /* Contenedor Principal */
        main {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Tarjeta Brainrot */
        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 8px ridge #00ff00;
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px #000;
            transform: rotate(-1deg);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: rotate(2deg) scale(1.02);
        }

        /* Título */
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #ff0000;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #ffcc00;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            animation: blink 0.8s infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            100% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(0.98); }
        }

        /* Galería de Memes (Responsiva) */
        .meme-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .meme-box {
            background: #000;
            border: 4px dashed #ff00ff;
            padding: 5px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .meme-box img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: contrast(150%) saturate(180%); /* Efecto Dank */
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }

        .meme-box img:hover {
            filter: invert(1);
            transform: spin;
        }

        .meme-caption {
            background: #fff;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 5px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        /* Texto Flotante */
        .subtext {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            background: #ffff00;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-top: 5px solid #ffcc00;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        footer span {
            color: #00ffff;
            animation: rainbow 2s infinite linear;
        }

        /* Animaciones extra goofy */
        .spinning-hardhat {
            font-size: 3rem;
            display: inline-block;
            animation: spin 1.5s infinite linear;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        /* Responsividad para pantallas chicas */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .card { padding: 15px; box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px #000; }
            body { background-size: 20px 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="hazard-bar"></div>

    <main>
        <div class="card">
            <span class="spinning-hardhat">👷‍♂️</span>
            <h1>¡ESTAMOS TRABAJANDO PARA USTED!</h1>
            <p style="font-weight: bold;">Mi compa el inge metiéndole mano al código fuente de la Matrix.</p>
            
            <div class="meme-grid">
                <div class="meme-box">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/1067/300/300" alt="Albañilería extrema">
                    <div class="meme-caption">Ingeniería nivel Dios 🧠🔥</div>
                </div>
                <div class="meme-box">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/1072/300/300" alt="Maquinaria pesada chistosa">
                    <div class="meme-caption">Cuando usas el 100% del cerebro 🏗️⚡</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="subtext">🚨 Se viene cositas (si no se cae el servidor) 🚨</div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div class="hazard-bar"></div>

    <footer>
        App created by <span>Juanech5</span>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
  
